window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Evil dragonriders are the worst.</b></p> <p>And the only ones who can defeat them are the good riders—the Dragon Elite.</p> <p><b>But fighting those who refuse to play by rules can be tricky.</b></p> <p>It’s difficult for Sophia Beaufont to get the upper hand when she refuses to loosen her morals.</p> <p><b>That’s exactly what makes her a Dragon Elite though.</b></p> <p>However, even if you’ve got angels on your side and fight for good, it doesn’t mean you’ll be successful.</p> <p><b>The Rogue Riders won’t stop until they’ve won.</b></p> <p>Or they are put down.</p> <p><b>Can Sophia stop the evil riders while also not starting a war that ends dragons forever? Or will they be forced to fight until there is no one left?</b></p>"; 
